{"tid":485404,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(背包JJ)伊朗 以色列入境一問","createTime":"2017-12-01T02:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T04:22:50.000Z","uid":115716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9410b9763c7f47b1f4ee369b10e243e4cd4c147","tid":485404,"uid":115716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"研究緊出年年頭去中東 以色列同伊朗都非常想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟想去完伊朗先入以色列 有無巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好驚入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f27409638dd85a6dc9e72ff5ba3e14c2b4eec5","tid":485404,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究緊出年年頭去中東 以色列同伊朗都非常想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟想去完伊朗先入以色列 有無巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好驚入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用兩本護照 bno 特衰"},{"pid":"9106e177da9b8c5a996b28e8fa7b5709d70fe6d0","tid":485404,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究緊出年年頭去中東 以色列同伊朗都非常想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟想去完伊朗先入以色列 有無巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好驚入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你遇咗入以色列之前做安檢會被人問好耐。我去以色列之前，護照有去馬來西亞、阿聯酋嘅記錄，佢地會捉住你去呢啲回教國家記錄重複問你問題。若果你本護照唔係只得伊朗出入境印的話，應該就無乜問題。"},{"pid":"12180d3f20d5caf3ee6803d06d7f1c45b2ee6613","tid":485404,"uid":99714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢去，有冇事"},{"pid":"6d11090adc25c981a11261d22c66512650a66346","tid":485404,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"樓主出發未？"},{"pid":"4d860cb70cf16e90866c8c891